It brings you with the fascinating interface, practical utilities, as well as extremely personalized and smooth operating experience.  Ready for a brand new operating experience on Android tablet Platform? Try it out!Features:Support dragging operation on dock barAdd / Delete screensSelf-define folders to categorize appsCheck running apps and clear all Brand new adding interfaceTips:1. Not able to install GO Launcher HD?GO Launcher HD is available for tablet devices with Android 2.2 or above. 2. How to add icons and widgets to home screen?Long press home screen or click Add icon on action bar to enter âAdd to screenâ interface. You can add app icons, shortcut, folder, widget to home screen. 3. How to change wallpaper?Long press home screen or click Add icon on action bar to enter âAdd to screenâ interface, and click Wallpaper tab and select wallpaper you want. 4. How to create app folder? You can create folders in two ways. First, click âNew Folderâ icon on action bar. reviews.title: Love it except..
reviews.comment: Go Launcher has always been the goto launcher for me but like others have mentioned, having to make multiple folders for my games is frustrating. Please take away the limit of apps per folder, it\'s a must for many of us! Would gladly change rating to 5 then!
reviews.author: Dale Epperson

reviews.title: Great, but...
reviews.comment: Where are the home screen scroll effects that I can customize on the phone version of this launcher?
reviews.author: Eli Schwartz

reviews.title: I love this launcher...
reviews.comment: However, I think the developers have forgotten about it.. Its been since November since it was updated.. :( They put a whole lot of focus on their phone launcher, which is understandable, but I think they should give some more love to this one. It also needs more themes.
reviews.author: Ben Diesel

reviews.title: So far average
reviews.comment: Missing some key features like effects and fonts. And only 2 themes..... Come on Go Launcher.. You can do better.
reviews.author: William Cordova

reviews.title: Fast
reviews.comment: This launcher works great! Nice, clean interface that runs very smooth on an Asus Transformer Pad TF300. Improved performance quite a bit!
reviews.author: Zackary Van Sickle

reviews.title: Cant theme
reviews.comment: I try to change the theme but whenever the theme store tries to load it throws me back to the home screen, what use is a launcher when you can\'t even add/change themes, right now for the galaxy tab 2 this app version is about as useful as a kettle with no plug!
reviews.author: Travis Clegg

reviews.title: Excellent
reviews.comment: Even better than my original but it needs to have more customization like go launcher ex like the custom fonts. Other than that it is the best launcher that I\'ve installed yet
reviews.author: jarrad weedman

reviews.title: Cannot open theme menu on my nexus 10 WiFi 32GB Rooted
reviews.comment: I am a paid customer and I can\'t even apply themes! When i click the theme bottom it opens and closes in the same second. This one could be great but since its free I guess the work goes into go launcher prime and next launcher. I have both and do not have this problem. On this tablet. But I don\'t want them I want the launcher HD. Please fix this major bug.
reviews.author: Dan Owens

reviews.title: Galaxy tablet 10.0
reviews.comment: Can not open any of my themes.  Would give it 5 stars if they worked. Love all the other features but the main reason I have ir is for the themes.
reviews.author: Melissa Craig

reviews.title: Not a great app
reviews.comment: Its not a great app as compared to go launcher ex for mobile phones.  No scope for customisation???  Overall ok app.
reviews.author: Neha s k

reviews.title: The Non-Tablet Version actually better on my tab!
reviews.comment: Can\'t customize Action bar.....hide status bar...unless I\'m doing it wrong, if so...ill stick to the older, dumbed down version.
reviews.author: Rudy A. Rimpel

reviews.title: The best for my Lenovo IdeaPad A1 tablet.
reviews.comment: Worked great under Android 2.3.4, but now with 4.0.4 works even better. My tablet is very responsive and fast now. Like a brand new tablet. I warmly recommend it to every tablet owner. Don\'t buy new tablet. Just install this free luncher. Plus, it looks wonderful. I wish I could give 10 stars.
reviews.author: Oktay Ahmed

reviews.title: almost perfect
reviews.comment: please add support for custom app on gestures and double click actions. also try to make icons bigger and sharper. even when set to big icons theyre still smalleer than default ics launcher
reviews.author: Remo Almeida

reviews.title: awesome!
reviews.comment: it fit perfectly on my galaxy tab 7 plus! app drawer looks amazing, and everything runs smooth like stock launcher!
reviews.author: Anderson Franca

reviews.comment: Excellent work again, guys I say when dev gave such master piece why the hell do you people crip for\tGreat work
reviews.author: Vishal Jadhav

reviews.title: Please read
reviews.comment: I have an Acer 500 and I have always used go launcher then I switched to this HD tablet version and it works but there are some bugs that need to be worked out please. For instance it always resets my wallpaper, it is a pic of my son from my gallery and it keeps switching back to the pic that came with the theme which is the dryad theme by the way. Also I have a tough time with the finger sliding to get to my alternate menus. Please fix and I will gladly give 5 stars. Thank you
reviews.author: Chris heup

reviews.title: Great App
reviews.comment: I just installed this on my new Asus Transformer - and it rocks. The slide action is soooooo smoooooth, I luv it! Maybe a few more themes plz?
reviews.author: Steve Palmer

reviews.title: Works well with my tablet
reviews.comment: I\'ve tried other launchers on my tablet and this is the best so far. I don\'t need a launcher with loads of customisable options, which makes this clean, simple, easy to use app, absolutely perfect for my use.
reviews.author: Tanja Drayton

reviews.title: Gesture options don\'t work
reviews.comment: On my tablet the all the finger swipe gestures don\'t work properly other than that pretty nice
reviews.author: A Google User
